  "translations": {
    "en": "Whenever God, Mighty and Majestic, intends to create the seed (nutfa) regarding which He took the covenant in the loins of Adam — or whatever He wills concerning it — and to place it in the womb, He stirs the man toward intercourse, and He reveals to the womb: 'Open your door so that My creation may enter you, and My irrevocable decree and My power [may be carried out].'",
